<p>
A <a href="/docs/Fields">field</a> implementing the Boolean <a href="/docs/Field_Types">field type</a> can store either <code>true</code> or <code>false</code>. The Boolean <a href="/docs/Field_Types">field type</a> has no parameters.
</p>

<div class="heading">Example Field</div>
<pre>{
	"Name" : "My Boolean Field",
	"Field Type" : "Boolean",
	"Description" : "The example usage of the Boolean Field Type.",
	"Required" : true,
	"Parameters" : {} 
}</pre>

<div class="heading">Example Value</div>
<pre>"ExampleUser.MyType.1" : {
	...
	"My Boolean Field" : true,
	...
}</pre>